trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to a tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data som er sendt til en Sporingstjenesten av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur når en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> samsvarer.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends a UserTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Når runtime sporing infrastruktur samsvarer med en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, sendes en UserTrackingRecord til Sporingstjenesten den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>som er forbundet med denne Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is required on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Sporingstjenesten kan utføre hvilken handling er nødvendig på dataene i sporing-post.

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av de angitte parameterne.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>for aktiviteter knyttet til bruker-hendelsen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.QualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for aktiviteter knyttet til bruker-hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: A number that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Et tall som identifiserer den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> for aktiviteter knyttet til bruker-hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: A number that identifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> of the parent activity of the activity associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Et tall som identifiserer den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> på overordnet aktivitet for aktiviteter knyttet til bruker-hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that indicates the date and time of the user event associated with the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>som angir dato og klokkeslett for brukeren hendelsen tilknyttet sporingsposten.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: The relative order in which the user event associated with this tracking record occurred in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Relativ rekkefølgen som hendelsen brukeren som er forbundet med denne oppføring sporing oppstod i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.target: En nøkkel som er tilknyttet brukerdataene for denne sporings-post eller en nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The user data associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Brukerdata som er knyttet til bruker-hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the common language runtime (CLR) type of the activity that emitted the user data for which this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"></xref> was created.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir common language runtime (CLR) typen aktivitet som slippes ut brukerdataene som denne <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref> ble opprettet.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity that emitted the user data.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>aktiviteten som slippes ut brukerdataene.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the user event.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av merknader som er knyttet til bruker-hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: You can specify annotations to be associated with a user event in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi merknader for å være knyttet til en bruker hendelse i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>, it returns these annotations in Annotations.
trans-unit.target: Når runtime sporing infrastruktur samsvarer med den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>, returneres disse merknader i merknader.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations that are associated with the user event by the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched in the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> som inneholder merknader som er knyttet til hendelsen brukeren av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> som passer i den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a list containing any additional data extracted from the workflow for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> that was matched.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste som inneholder flere data som er hentet fra arbeidsflyten for den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> som passer.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure can extract data from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Når en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>samsvarer, kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur kan trekke ut data fra arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The data to be extracted is specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Dataene som skal trekkes ut er angitt i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> can contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects, which specify member data to be extracted from the activity associated with the user event, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects, which specify member data to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kan inneholde <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objekter, som angir medlemsdata som skal trekkes ut aktivitet som er knyttet til bruker-hendelsen, og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekter, som angir medlemsdata som skal trekkes ut aktiviteten roten av arbeidsflyten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Each type of extract can also specify annotations to be returned with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Hver type extract kan også angi merknader som skal returneres med utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure encapsulates each piece of extracted data and its associated annotations in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> which it adds to Body.
trans-unit.target: Kjøring sporing infrastruktur innkapsler hver del av utpakkede data og tilknyttede merknader i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>som legges til i meldingsteksten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: Because the user data pushed to the tracking service by the user event is contained in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>, Body will frequently be an empty list.
trans-unit.target: Fordi brukerdataene sendt til Sporingstjenesten av hendelsen brukeren finnes i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>, Body blir ofte en tom liste.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: A list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> objects each of which contains a single piece of extracted data and its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: En liste over <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> objekter som inneholder ett enkelt utpakkede data og tilknyttede merknader.

trans-unit.source: Context of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Konteksten til aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: A number that identifies the context of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Et tall som identifiserer konteksten til aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: Always a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic) for a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Alltid nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic) for en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: There is no event data associated with a user event, therefore, EventArgs has no meaning and is always a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: Det er ingen Hendelsesdata som er knyttet til en bruker-hendelse, derfor EventArgs kan ingen mening og er alltid en nullreferanse (`Nothing`).

trans-unit.source: The user data that is pushed to the runtime tracking infrastructure by whichever one of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A> methods that caused the user event is sent in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Dataene for brukeren som er sendt til kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur av en hvilken som helst i <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A>eller <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A>metoder som forårsaket hendelsen bruker sendes i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Any data extracts that are associated with the user event by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> are encapsulated in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> objects and sent in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Uttrekk alle data som er tilknyttet hendelsen brukeren som <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>er inkludert i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>objekter og sendt i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.target: En nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) for en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order of the user event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir rekkefølgen av hendelsen brukeren som samsvarer med den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the order of the user event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> relative to the other tracking events emitted by the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder angir rekkefølgen av hendelsen brukeren som samsvarer med den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>i forhold til andre sporing hendelsene slippes ut av arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder will be unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder vil være unike innenfor en arbeidsflytforekomst, men garanteres ikke være sammenhengende.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir rekkefølgen av hendelsen brukeren i arbeidsflytforekomsten.
